Want to contribute to the wiki by editing and making pages? Great! 

# Making an account

To contribute to the hku.one wiki, you will need to create an account first. 

To do so, click on 'edit' on any page > password > fill in a username and password > register. At the moment, 'email' and 'openid' don't work as login options.

Now you can go to any page and edit its contents!

